{"tid":781473,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係唔係個個都岩橙色眼影架屌你老尾","createTime":"2018-08-16T02:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T15:15:13.000Z","uid":128894,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b30a2c0e44acd8cf53010f9f914207819796d15e","tid":781473,"uid":128894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:15:21.000Z","msg":"唔知幾時開始興啲橙色粉紅色眼影<br />\n啲女就起度跟風<br />\n唔撚岩自己都要達落隻死人眼度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到隻眼腫撚左咁<br />\n真係好撚樣衰<br />\n<br />\n日尻日返工見撚到條女化到塊面腫哂咁<br />\n唔識化又亂達啲野上塊面<br />\n又浮哂粉甩撚哂皮咁<br />\n又橙色眼影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟何來的自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/101445_a63107f4d3ccc33ff3a1fe7aeea609e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F101445_a63107f4d3ccc33ff3a1fe7aeea609e0.png&h=0ac3daaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/101447_5ad3e91c67a3ad7e134af78f01618fd8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F101447_5ad3e91c67a3ad7e134af78f01618fd8.png&h=9e8658b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求下你地唔好再亂咁擺啲顏色上塊面度<br />\n去厠所照下鏡先出門口<br />\n人地化得靚唔代表你都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好撚柒<br />\n寧願你地化返啲mk妝"},{"pid":"7dea2069bde7fcfe95073a83d72f533ac75457b1","tid":781473,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1